#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.84"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.84:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.84:0.2"
msgid "9. Samaṇavagga"
msgstr "9. Ascetics"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.84:0.3"
msgid "84. Vajjiputtasutta"
msgstr "84. The Vajji"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.84:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Vesālī, at the Great Wood, in the "
"hall with the peaked roof."

msgctxt "an3.84:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro vajjiputtako bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno "
"kho so vajjiputtako bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then a certain Vajji monk went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one "
"side, and said to him:"

msgctxt "an3.84:1.3"
msgid ""
"“sādhikamidaṃ, bhante, diyaḍḍhasikkhāpadasataṃ anvaddhamāsaṃ uddesaṃ "
"āgacchati."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, each fortnight over a hundred and fifty training rules are recited."

msgctxt "an3.84:1.4"
msgid "Nāhaṃ, bhante, ettha sakkomi sikkhitun”ti."
msgstr "I’m not able to train in them.”"

msgctxt "an3.84:1.5"
msgid "“Sakkhissasi pana tvaṃ, bhikkhu, tīsu sikkhāsu sikkhituṃ—"
msgstr "“But monk, are you able to train in three trainings:"

msgctxt "an3.84:1.6"
msgid "adhisīlasikkhāya, adhicittasikkhāya adhipaññāsikkhāyā”ti?"
msgstr "the higher ethics, the higher mind, and the higher wisdom?”"

msgctxt "an3.84:1.7"
msgid "“Sakkomahaṃ, bhante, tīsu sikkhāsu sikkhituṃ—"
msgstr "“I am, sir.”"

msgctxt "an3.84:1.8"
msgid "adhisīlasikkhāya, adhicittasikkhāya, adhipaññāsikkhāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.84:1.9"
msgid "“Tasmātiha tvaṃ, bhikkhu, tīsu sikkhāsu sikkhassu—"
msgstr "“So, monk, you should train in these three trainings:"

msgctxt "an3.84:1.10"
msgid "adhisīlasikkhāya, adhicittasikkhāya, adhipaññāsikkhāya."
msgstr "the higher ethics, the higher mind, and the higher wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.84:2.1"
msgid ""
"Yato kho tvaṃ, bhikkhu, adhisīlampi sikkhissasi, adhicittampi sikkhissasi, "
"adhipaññampi sikkhissasi, tassa tuyhaṃ bhikkhu adhisīlampi sikkhato "
"adhicittampi sikkhato adhipaññampi sikkhato rāgo pahīyissati, doso "
"pahīyissati, moho pahīyissati."
msgstr "As you train in these, you will give up greed, hate, and delusion."

msgctxt "an3.84:2.2"
msgid ""
"So tvaṃ rāgassa pahānā dosassa pahānā mohassa pahānā yaṃ akusalaṃ na taṃ "
"karissasi, yaṃ pāpaṃ na taṃ sevissasī”ti."
msgstr "Then you won’t do anything unskillful, or practice anything bad.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.231"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.84:3.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho so bhikkhu aparena samayena adhisīlampi sikkhi, adhicittampi "
"sikkhi, adhipaññampi sikkhi."
msgstr ""
"After some time that monk trained in the higher ethics, the higher mind, and "
"the higher wisdom."

msgctxt "an3.84:3.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa adhisīlampi sikkhato adhicittampi sikkhato adhipaññampi sikkhato rāgo "
"pahīyi, doso pahīyi, moho pahīyi."
msgstr "He gave up greed, hate, and delusion."

msgctxt "an3.84:3.3"
msgid ""
"So rāgassa pahānā dosassa pahānā mohassa pahānā yaṃ akusalaṃ taṃ nākāsi, yaṃ "
"pāpaṃ taṃ na sevīti."
msgstr "Then he didn’t do anything unskillful, or practice anything bad."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.84:3.4"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
